  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Heat the wok or skillet until the oil is almost smoking.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and stir-fry until fragrant.",
    "Add the soy sauce, oyster sauce, rice vinegar, and sugar.",
    "Stir-fry the sauce for 1-2 minutes, or until it has thickened slightly.",
